, N'paritranaya--for the deliverance; sadhunam--of the devotees; vinasaya-- for the annihilation; ca--also; duskrtam--of the miscreants; dharma-- principles of religion; samsthapana-arthaya--to reestablish;sambhavami--I do appear; yuge--millennium; yuge--after millennium. '
